  "subject": "Chore: Update RTD and tox config for ubuntu-24.04",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Update RTD and tox config for ubuntu-24.04\n\nUpdate .readthedocs.yaml to ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13, replacing the\ndeprecated ubuntu-20.04 image and EOL Python 3.8.\n\nSwitch tox.ini from remote upper-constraints URL to a local\netc/upper-constraints.onap.txt file, avoiding build failures when\ngit.onap.org returns HTTP 500 errors.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: I1b6283ed150e8f51a8127325909686e771c1afb6\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
